column1: return_core_on_title;Enable 'Return Cores' decisions;;;;;;;;;;;;x
return_core_on_desc;The Return Cores decisions allow you to return cores of vassals and spherelings
column2: as long as you don't have a core in the province
column3: and are otherwise kept hidden from view to avoid having them clutter up your decision list.;;;;;;;;;;;;x
